questions.question: An object o0 is shaped like a cylinder. In a subsequent sequence lasting at least 10 frames, an object o1 is behind another object o2, o0 is on the left side of the video frame, and o0 is near o2. Finally, for another duration of at least 10 frames, o1 is behind o0 and o0 is behind o2, while o2 is shaped like a sphere.
questions.dsl: Shape_cylinder(o0); Duration((Behind(o1, o2), Left(o0), Near(o0, o2)), 10); Duration((Behind(o0, o2), Behind(o1, o0), Shape_sphere(o2)), 10)

questions.question: An object o0 is initially in front of another object o1. Then, o0 is at the bottom of the frame, and o1 is far from o0 and made of metal. Finally, for at least 10 frames, an object o2 is on the left side of the frame, o0 is on the right side, and o1 is shaped like a cylinder.
questions.dsl: FrontOf(o0, o1); (Bottom(o0), Far(o1, o0), Material_metal(o1)); Duration((Left(o2), Right(o0), Shape_cylinder(o1)), 10)

questions.question: For at least 5 frames, a blue object o0 is in front of o1, and o1 is to the right of a third object o2. Then, for a duration of at least 15 frames, o0 is on the left side of the video frame, o1 is to the right of o0 and on the right side of the frame, and o2 is shaped like a cylinder.
questions.dsl: Duration((Color_blue(o0), FrontOf(o0, o1), RightOf(o1, o2)), 5); Duration((Left(o0), RightOf(o1, o0), Right(o1), Shape_cylinder(o2)), 15)

questions.question: For at least 10 frames, a cylinder-shaped object o0 is far away from another object o1, and a third object o2 is on the right side of the video frame. Then, in a subsequent moment, o2 is behind o0, is yellow in color, and is in front of o1, with o1 being at the top of the frame.
questions.dsl: Duration((Far(o0, o1), Right(o2), Shape_cylinder(o0)), 10); (Behind(o2, o0), Color_yellow(o2), FrontOf(o1, o2), Top(o1))

questions.question: For at least 5 frames, an object o0 is both behind and to the left of another object o1, and o0 is also at the top of the frame. Then, for another 5 frames, o0 is on the left side of the frame while o1 is at the top. Finally, for a duration of at least 10 frames, o1 is green and o0 is shaped like a cylinder.
questions.dsl: Duration((Behind(o0, o1), LeftOf(o0, o1), Top(o0)), 5); Duration((Left(o0), Top(o1)), 5); Duration((Color_green(o1), Shape_cylinder(o0)), 10)

questions.question: For at least 15 frames, an object o0 is behind another object o1. Then, o0 is made of metal, and a third object o2 is shaped like a cylinder. Finally, o0 is behind o2, o1 is at the bottom of the frame, o2 is far away from o0, and o2 is to the right of o1.
questions.dsl: Duration(Behind(o0, o1), 15); (Material_metal(o0), Shape_cylinder(o2)); (Behind(o0, o2), Bottom(o1), Far(o2, o0), RightOf(o2, o1))

questions.question: For at least 15 frames, an object o0 is behind and to the left of another object o1, and o0 is also at the bottom of the frame, while a third object o2 is made of rubber. In this segment, o0 is shaped like a cylinder. Following that, for another duration of at least 15 frames, o2 is behind o0, and o1 is to the right of o0.
questions.dsl: Duration((Behind(o0, o1), Bottom(o0), LeftOf(o0, o1), Material_rubber(o2)), 15); Shape_cylinder(o0); Duration((Behind(o2, o0), RightOf(o1, o0)), 15)

questions.question: For at least 15 frames, two cylinder-shaped objects o0 and o2 are near each other, with o2 to the right of o1 and o2 at the top of the frame. Subsequently, for at least 10 frames, o0 is to the right of o1. Then, for a duration of at least 5 frames, o1 is behind o2.
questions.dsl: Duration((Near(o0, o1), RightOf(o2, o1), Shape_cylinder(o0), Shape_cylinder(o2), Top(o2)), 15); Duration(RightOf(o0, o1), 10); Duration(Behind(o1, o2), 5)

questions.question: For at least 15 frames, a cylinder-shaped object o0 is behind another object o1, and o0 is also at the top of the frame while o2 is on the left side of the frame. Then, for at least 10 frames, o1 is gray, o2 is far from o1, and o1 is to the right of o0.
questions.dsl: Duration((Behind(o0, o1), Left(o2), Shape_cylinder(o0), Top(o0)), 15); Duration((Color_gray(o1), Far(o2, o1), RightOf(o1, o0)), 10)

questions.question: For at least 10 frames, an object o0 is far from and to the right of another object o1, while a third object o2 is shaped like a cylinder. Then, for at least 5 frames, o2 is far from o1, and o1 is also shaped like a cylinder. Finally, o2 is near o0 and is at the top of the frame.
questions.dsl: Duration((Far(o0, o1), RightOf(o0, o1), Shape_cylinder(o2)), 10); Duration((Far(o2, o1), Shape_cylinder(o1)), 5); (Near(o2, o0), Top(o2))
